As the dust cleared a figure stood, gun in hand shield in other.  It was Ultimo.  His shield pulsed with extreme energy.  

"Hellpeon, you aren't the only one that can absorb energy." he said as he held the shield against his chest he whispered, 'release'. A large stream of energy flowed from the shield at Hellpeon.  At the same time his gun shot 25 shots from the auto rifle.
